'''Escalation''', or '''elevation''', was a ceremony of promotion among the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. When a Yuuzhan Vong earned the right to be escalated, they would sacrifice a [[Limb/Legends|limb]], which the [[Shaper caste|shapers]] would then replace with that of a creature native to [[Yuuzhan'tar]]. If the ceremony was successful, then that Yuuzhan Vong was favored by the gods, and allowed to advance. However, if the [[Priest caste|priests]] found a flaw or the implant was rejected, the Yuuzhan Vong was then declared a [[Shamed Ones|Shamed One]], and passed to the lowest levels of society.

While it was believed that rejection was because of the gods' anger, in truth it was the incompetence of the shaper who performed the escalation. However, on certain occasions, a shaper would intentionally cause an implant rejection, as was done by a [[Master Shaper]] [[Mezhan Kwaad]] to her former lover [[Vua Rapuung]].

